AFD.desc: Far-right political party in Germany (German: "Alternative für Deutschland").

auf1.desc: AUF1 (German original: "Alternatives Unabhängiges Fernsehen, Kanal 1") is an Austrian online media platform / website. Public reference and media sources discuss AUF1 in relation to misinformation/conspiracy narratives and regulatory issues concerning broadcasting without authorization. (Sources: auf1-wiki-de; auf1-wiki-en; tagesschau-auf1-desinformation; kommaustria-auf1tv-2023-05-17)

1161.desc: Numeric code used in far-right contexts meaning "Anti-Antifascist Action" (German original: "Anti-Antifaschistische Aktion", often shortened "Anti-Antifa"), i.e. opposition to antifascist movements. (Source: Wikipedia page "Rechtsextreme Symbole und Zeichen".)
